⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Demandred
node WOT · WOT · ⟦Demandred:WOT:afdbc1⟧

WHO   — Demandred — the general consumed by the Dragon's shadow
WHAT  — One of the Forsaken — a brilliant statesman and general of the Age of Legends, second to Lews Therin in nearly everything.
WHERE — WOT · The Wheel of Time  Framework inputs: the Shadow  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — His envy of the Dragon is the Shadow's purest mirror of the hero — talent ruined by the refusal to be second.
HOW   — He turned to the Shadow out of jealousy, later conquered and ruled the eastern land of Shara in secret, and arrived at the Last Battle as its mightiest commander.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  Second to the Dragon in everything but hatred — and first in that.

